<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
      
      img {
        padding-top: 3%;
}
html,
body {
  background-color: #eaeaea;
  font: 400 1rem/1.625rem "Open Sans", sans-serif;
}

.transition {
  transition: .3s cubic-bezier(.3, 0, 0, 1.3)
}

.card {
  background-color: #fff;
  height: 600px;
  width: 500px;
  position: absolute;
  margin: auto;
  top: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  overflow: hidden;
}
.gg{
  display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-left:40px;
    padding-right:40px;
    
    margin-top: -5px;
}
.gg1{
  display: flex;
    justify-content: left;
    padding-left:30px;
    padding-right:30px;
    margin-top: -10px;
}
.aa{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: left;
    text-align:left;
    color:black;
    padding-left:30px;
    padding-right:30px;
    margin-top: -20px;
}

.bbb{
  display: flex;
  justify-content: left;
  text-align: left;
  padding-top:3%;
  color: #545252;
  padding-left:30px;
    padding-right:30px;
   
}

.dd{
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: left;
  color: #545252;
  margin-top: -40px;
  padding-left:0px;
    padding-right:40px;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="gg">
          <img  src="https://template.preview.drcstudio.co.in/logo.png" alt="" width="60px" height="60px">
          </div>
          <div class="gg">
          <h1>Anya Healthcare</h1>
          </div>

            <div class="gg1">
              <h4>Hi {{name}},</h4>

              </div>
              <div class="gg1">
                <h4>Your account has been canceled. We're really sorry to see you go! </h4>
                </div>

                <div class="aa">
                    <h5>This email confirms that your appoinment has been canceled.<br>We're really sorry to see you go,but thanks for giving us a try.</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="aa">
                    <h5>If you feel any difficulties,We do our best to make sure our service is accessible and reliable.</h5>
                </div>


              
                <div class="bbb" >
                    <h5>Thanks for being a part of our community.<br>We hope to see you around.</h5>
                  </div>
                  <div class="dd">
                    <h5>If you did not request this, please contact healthcare center.<br>Thanks {{name}}.</h5> 
                  </div>
        </div>
           
</body>
